jcr:content.jcr:title: PA for Fall Product Kick-off at the Armada

data.address: 301 A Philip Randolph Blvd., Jacksonville, FL 32202
data.details:
Help younger girls learn about goal setting, money management, safety, customer service and more!!  Lead hands on activities and games while sharing your fall product knowledge, plus you get a special Armada themed SWAP, a chance to earn an Armada FC patch and participate in an Armada FC community project.  Food and beverage will be provided prior to the Armada game!

** Girls must be PA trained to register for this session.  Participating PAâ€™s will earn 5 service hours.

**Family members who wish to attend, please register using the non-PA Armada event.

The last day to register for this event - August 1, 2015 (there will be no extensions or walk-up registrations).

No refunds once registration is confirmed

Financial assistance is not available for this event
